sections.text:
Walking with the Lord—what splendor!
Dawn shines forth to greet the day;
Each step, to His voice surrender;
Every moment take His way.

Walk with Him—naught can alarm us,
Though assailed from many sides;
Step by step obey His guidance;
Narrow path, where’er He guides.

Walk with Him—our future’s precious;
With Him we’ll His kingdom gain;
Every step, pursue His purpose,
On His narrow way remain.
